						<summary>

						<p>On a red-stone slab set up in front of the Śiva temple.</p>						

						<p>Dated [Śaka] 1179, <hi rend="italic">Piṅgaḷa, Māgha,</hi> ba. 15, Monday, corresponding to A.D. 1258, January 6. The week-day was Sunday.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Records a gift of 1 <hi rend="italic">puṭṭi</hi> of land by Chandaladēvi to god Ēlēśvara.</p>						

